      "description": "FEA-predicted construct stiffness compared against experimental measurements from 11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. All predictions fell within the <10% QoI difference acceptance bound; normalized validation metric E/uval = 0.84 (< 1.96 threshold)."
